name: RNR_015 - BLUE SUNFLOWER
description:
A mind's eye reflects on a blue sunflower's evolution. 

Analog video feedback loop using an RCA T09085 television and a Samsung SCL810 camcorder with built-in digital mirror effect. Minor digital color correction. 

Music created improvisationally with KORG Minilogue and ZOOM G1-on direct to cassette tape.
